                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">现在大家都把秦始皇想的很坏 但其实秦始皇算是一个好皇帝了 在众多皇帝中我最欣赏的就是秦始皇了 他这一生也做了很多了不起的事 虽说他暴政 但他确实适合是统治六国的人</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1141936845">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1141936845" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1141936845" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1141936845">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/156850607/">ORANGE</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2017-01-25</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">多数人只会在看到“秦始皇”三个字后立马浮现“暴君”二字.却很少有人去分析在秦始皇所处的时代中,他为什么这样做.对于写秦朝写秦始皇的书中,作者们都会去解析“秦始皇现象”.这本书更是深刻的去解析了这一现象.也正是因为剖析得深刻,所以会有一些难懂之处.需要认真品读.</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1124027633">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1124027633" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1124027633" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1124027633">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/74999180/">Matt先森</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2016-12-21</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">千古一帝。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1066898339">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1066898339" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1066898339" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1066898339">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/cherryJ/">白骨</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2016-07-27</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">四星慰劳作者学术性的研究，整篇论文即视感。故事性不强</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1050423908">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1050423908" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1050423908" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1050423908">有用</a>
